{"title":"南浔镇","authors":["陈山"],"dates":[{"year":1963,"month":2,"day":17}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"南浔镇"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"陈山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万家膏血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"东南财富，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑成了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"江浙财阀的乐园，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋姓独夫的禁囿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"养肥了四象、八牛、七十二只金毛狗〔注〕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"几十年间，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"横冲直撞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发疯劲向人民搏斗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"平原旭日初腾，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"照射旧王朝的遗迹；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这一切，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都化成了墓前石兽。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清波浮着绿野，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿野载着红楼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"登临极目："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好一领堆金叠翠的雀毛裘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"由勇晴雯辛劳缀补，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从今回到人民手。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看船刺花针、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"河盘彩线；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"稻米流脂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"鱼鲜组绣；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"绿茸茸的是青菜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白晃晃的是丝绸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"月洞桥边总收口。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"春花秋月庆丰收，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"苦尽甘来味深厚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听嘹亮歌声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"唱有字无腔曲调："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“摆主人公身份，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完成了国家收购！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"闹市中心船靠岸，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"白鸽子般的干净，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迎来一对笑姑娘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"招公社农民沽酒。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六二年十一月十五日，南浔镇上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔注〕为解放前本镇富豪们的称号"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}